STAFF.name: Denver Bohling
STAFF.bio: Denver Bohling is a web developer originally from Laramie, WY. He moved here in June 2015 with interests to expand his horizons and explore Portland's budding music scene. Some of his favorite musical effects include heavy fuzz, chorus, and modulated delay. Denver touts a strong interest in shenanigans, grade school-level hijinks, tomfoolery, and general bafoonery.
